Assistant Resturent Manager and Supervisor
- ,
Date Posted: 2014/05/04 14:50:06
Ref. JB3047178
Job Description
A high end Food and Beverage company with ambitious growth plans
is looking for a Restaurant supervisor to assist with the overall operations of the restaurant. This position offers a highly competitive salary and package which includes; live in or out allowance, uniform, laundry services, meals during working hours, flight allowance, medical coverage etc. If you are looking to be part of a growing organization that values its employees this is your opportunity to prove yourself. They are looking to open 30 restaurants in the next three years. The supervisor position will be based in Abu Dhabi and possibility to be later in Dubai
Skills
•High school diploma or higher education .
•Minimum 1 year experience as supervisor in a restaurant or hotel
•Team player able to work with different nationalities
